com.procom.filefly

Class SendFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • com.procom.filefly.SendFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChooseFileDialogFragment.ChooseFileDialogListener

    public class SendFragment
extends Fragment
implements ChooseFileDialogFragment.ChooseFileDialogListener
    Inflates the user interface for the "Sends" tab.

    SenderFragment creates the user interface for the "Sends" tab of MainActivity and implements a button to open a dialog for selecting a file to be transferred via the NFC Android Beam API.

    This class implements android.view.View.OnClickListener in order to process button clicks.

    Author:
    Peter Piech
